This appears to be some kind of a dictionary for ancient arcane languages. Within is a handwritten note:

"I have decided to use the Unuraakil language for the special-purpose golems. I'll just have to make sure that they frequently remind me of their numbers, as I will need them for their maintenance.

It seems my attempts at creating intelligence have had more success than I thought. The golems have worked out that both changing their numbers AND the Unuraakil word standing for each number is an excellent strategy to confound would-be intruders and prevent others from using the maintenance machine. While this is excellent news for my progress and dealing with those Duergar nuisances, I now have to find which bookshelf they hid their 'redesigned' Unuraakil words on to work out what to put into the maintenance machine..."
